Gil Gonzales Manalo Just be reminded folks that during this time of the year there is a high pressure located in Northern Japan pushing any weather disturbance downwards. But since it is dynamic kapag humina ang high pressure na ito, typhoons will have the tendencies to go up north but kapag lumakas uli eh i push nya pababa ang mga ito resulting to a zigzag pattern in their path.
